When entering story part...

1. with save/load system
present load page
(else: if new player, start from the beginning)
(continue until end of story)
[game-status: record both current 1 progress position + current game-data]

2. without save/load system
present all entries for volumes/chapters/parts
(when finish the current small unit, return to this selection-page)
[game-status: record 1 progress-save-point]

3. branch selection (* consider later as extra)
present all the experienced paths and branches, allow reselect
[game-status: record each checkpoint's game-data set; multiple game-data sets on multiple game-progress points]


